# Implementation Plan - Premium UI/UX & Spacing Reduction

## Goal Description
The objective is to overhaul the application layout to look more "premium" and "compact" by reducing the overall scale, reducing sidebar width, and tightening the spacing between widgets by 40-50%.

## User Review Required
> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Global Scale Strategy**: I propose using a CSS `zoom: 0.9` (90% scale) on the `html` tag. This is the most effective way to "reduce the scale of the entire application" uniformly. 
> Alternatively, we can reduce the base font-size, but that may not affect fixed-pixel elements. `zoom` is verified to work well for this specific "density" request in modern browsers.

> [!WARNING]
> **Sidebar Width**: Reducing sidebar from 240px to 200px. This might require adjusting long navigation titles or icons.

## Proposed Changes

### Global Styles
#### [MODIFY] [globals.css](file:///Users/siddiqueahmed/Desktop/AI/Alsonotify/alsonotify-frontend/src/styles/globals.css)
-   Add `html { zoom: 0.90; }` (or `transform: scale(0.9)` with origin top-left if zoom has issues, but zoom is better for layout reflow).
-   Update `--radius` if necessary to match the new denser look (e.g., reduce slightly if it looks too round).

### Layout Components
#### [MODIFY] [AlsonotifyLayoutWrapper.tsx](file:///Users/siddiqueahmed/Desktop/AI/Alsonotify/alsonotify-frontend/src/app/AlsonotifyLayoutWrapper.tsx)
-   Change sidebar width logic: `w-[240px]` -> `w-[200px]`.
-   Reduce main content gap: `gap-5` (20px) -> `gap-3` (12px).
-   Reduce main content padding: `p-5` -> `p-3`.

#### [MODIFY] [Sidebar.tsx](file:///Users/siddiqueahmed/Desktop/AI/Alsonotify/alsonotify-frontend/src/components/common/Sidebar.tsx)
-   Adjust internal padding and icon sizing if needed to fit the new `200px` width.

### Dashboard Pages
#### [MODIFY] [dashboard/page.tsx](file:///Users/siddiqueahmed/Desktop/AI/Alsonotify/alsonotify-frontend/src/app/dashboard/page.tsx)
-   Reduce grid/flex gaps: `gap-5` -> `gap-3`.
-   This affects the spacing between Progress, Notes, Meetings, and Leaves widgets.

### Widgets (Sample)
#### [MODIFY] [MeetingsWidget.tsx](file:///Users/siddiqueahmed/Desktop/AI/Alsonotify/alsonotify-frontend/src/components/dashboard/MeetingsWidget.tsx)
-   Reduce container padding: `p-5` -> `p-4` or `p-3`.
-   Reduce internal list gaps: `gap-2.5` -> `gap-1.5` or `gap-2`.
-   (Will apply similar changes to `ProgressWidget`, `NotesWidget`, `LeavesWidget` as discovered).

## Design Tokens (Premium Look)
-   **Density**: High (Compact).
-   **Radius**: `20px` or `16px` (down from `24px` to fit tighter spacing).
-   **Shadows**: Ensure `shadow-sm` or custom subtle shadows are used instead of heavy drop shadows.

## Verification Plan

### Manual Verification
-   **Visual Check**: Open the dashboard and verify:
    -   Is the sidebar narrower?
    -   Are widgets closer together?
    -   Does the text look readable at 90% scale?
    -   Do hover states and dropdowns still align correctly?
-   **Responsive Check**: Ensure the layout doesn't break on smaller laptop screens (13" / 1280px).
